  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1479962/" class="title-link">太深了 看不懂</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1479962"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2809402/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2809402-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2809402/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">SANG</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-08-25"
      class="main-meta">2008-08-25 20:47:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1479962_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  今年的某天，又把这本书拿起，说她是一本文集，更不如说是研究作者理论的指导，毕竟她代表的是中国国际关系理论发展的指向标，看这本的时候，你不得不要有深厚的国际关系大模块下的背景知识，要不，和我一样，真的太深，看的累，也怪我学识薄浅。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1479962/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
